---
import AnimatedSection from "./AnimatedSection";
---

<section id="about" class="border-t border-border bg-bg-alt py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
    <AnimatedSection client:visible>
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
        About
      </h2>
    </AnimatedSection>

    <AnimatedSection client:visible>
      <h3 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-primary md:text-4xl">
        A bit about me
      </h3>
    </AnimatedSection>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <AnimatedSection client:visible>
        <p>
          I'm a Software Engineer who enjoys building tools that solve real problems —
          whether that's open-source projects, self-hosted infrastructure, or
          applications that make life easier. I'm always looking for new ways to
          learn and improve.
        </p>
      </AnimatedSection>

      <AnimatedSection client:visible>
        <p>
          Outside of work, I spend a lot of time tinkering with my homelab setup,
          exploring new technologies, and contributing to open source. I believe in
          sharing knowledge, which is why I write about the things I build and the
          lessons I learn along the way.
        </p>
      </AnimatedSection>

      <AnimatedSection client:visible>
        <p>
          When I'm not coding, you'll probably find me automating something that
          doesn't need automating, or going down a rabbit hole of Docker containers.
        </p>
      </AnimatedSection>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
